咩分別<br />\n<br />\n依加香港擺到明正面上街抗爭就完全唔夠個政府打，所以最大效益既方法就係打國際線，所以唔可以得罪其他國家同佢地既人，（尤其美台，但投左共嗰d eg. 新加坡 例外啦），依加小小一個Toyz 事件就開post話成個台灣民族低賤，傳左過去會點諗？<br />\n<br />\n屌都唔知樓主係咪五毛黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a0a42114ba9c5de247c3f38b01fa20c4014e20","tid":2041030,"uid":182860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:30:08.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"3113595759667aff68cf107a8ed245c89318db04","tid":2041030,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f6e60c6026263060b95b873c01ddcb207207fa","tid":2041030,"uid":193642,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"網上咩人都有，拒絕互屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n垃圾Po"},{"pid":"95497e332127dbce37d1cd6c00d702a455ba7e03","tid":2041030,"uid":358696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2170138fe665e5158062179df4f78039cef9de24","tid":2041030,"uid":60916,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"fcfe75fd40eb79ac88d47b6076f37f7e464818e9","tid":2041030,"uid":48083,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:36:08.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能<br />\n<br />\n諗深一層，攬炒巴係一群（個）咩人我地都唔知，點解仲有咁多傻鳩入錢比佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2040640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2040640</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"次次駁唔到就一句五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"如果你唔係五毛 都係三毛狗一隻。"},{"pid":"3f3f9ae7d25091173edb4463fc7d9ca5ea414143","tid":2041030,"uid":33565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:30:53.000Z","msg":"周圍辣火頭"},{"pid":"c14201957e19e4fce6c02a8fa1890745c6eed2aa","tid":2041030,